videos.description: Devwah Whaley bounces off a tackler and scores from 5 yards out.
videos.headline: Whaley swims in for the Arkansas score

videos.description: Tyler Keane hits Omar Black on a back shoulder fade for the score.
videos.headline: Keane throws a strike for Chanticleers TD

videos.description: Alex James gives Coastal Carolina the lead with a 6-yard plunge.
videos.headline: James pounds it in for another Chanticleers score

videos.description: T.J. Hammonds springs the screen pass for a 60-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Hammonds rips off long catch-and-run TD for Razorbacks

videos.description: Arkansas' Jonathan Nance catches a Hail Mary pass off of two separate deflections, but is just short of the end zone.
videos.headline: Crazy Hail Mary tip drill falls a yard short

videos.description: Kilton  Anderson throws to Marcus Williamson who jumps up for the 40-yard grab.
videos.headline: Coastal Carolina's Anderson airs it out to Williamson

videos.description: Kilton Anderson finds Marcus Williamson in the corner of the end zone to give Coastal Carolina the lead.
videos.headline: Anderson lobs up a Caostal Carolina TD pass

videos.description: Nicholas Clark picks up the dropped backwards pass and takes it 31 yards to the house.
videos.headline: Chanticleers scoop and score

videos.description: Austin Cantrell runs right up the middle for 5-yard score.
videos.headline: Cantrell walks in for an Arkansas TD

videos.description: Kilton Anderson hits Chris Jones on a 10-yard out for the score.
videos.headline: Anderson fires a strike for Coastal Carolina TD

videos.description: T.J. Hammonds sprints his way 88 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Hammonds takes off for long Arkansas TD

videos.description: QB Cole Kelley called his own number from a yard out to give Arkansas the lead.
videos.headline: Kelley pounds it in for Arkansas TD

videos.description: Arkansas relied on the run game to claw their way back to victory and avoid a monumental upset.
videos.headline: Arkansas escapes against Coastal Carolina
